description2:
Glenburn Darjeeling First Flush: Made of only the finest tender shoots   and an abundance of silver tip; 
Himalayan Green Tea: A naturally sweet Green bright infusion. Light lemon yellow cup, smooth and buttery with fresh zesty undertones; 
Khongea Assam Golden Tips: The best of Assam teas, this distinctive tea is grown only in a few tea plantations;
Royal Bengal Masala Chai: Khongea CTC harvested during the high-quality Second Flush period in Assam. Delicious tea with ginger,black pepper, cinnamon, cardamom pods and cloves.
